  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426710/extras/c82f945db616549260b0c897b1755155.avif?t=1721093505\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>A doctor in a small town suddenly gained the ability to shrink his body, so he shrunk his body into various patients' bodies and treated diseases by eliminating the virus in the patients' bodies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426710/extras/5a509c6f871f83a83e97aff7af3d2286.avif?t=1721093505\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dominating Summon Combat: Although the Doctor himself has some attack ability, he mainly needs to fight through summons.<br></li><li>Cooperate with summons to trigger skills.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426710/extras/0a0e55ccb391ee845439a8c85d416633.poster.avif?t=1721093505\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426710/extras/0a0e55ccb391ee845439a8c85d416633.webm?t=1721093505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426710/extras/0a0e55ccb391ee845439a8c85d416633.mp4?t=1721093505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Each summon has its own special attack mode, which can be upgraded and synthesized to create a more powerful summon.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426710/extras/983ed675f9caedef8acbcccc4389836f.avif?t=1721093505\" width=600 height=238 /></span><br></li><li>The Doctor can choose a base weapon, and different summons will activate different characteristics of the weapon, such as ejection, explosion, burning, freezing, etc.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426710/extras/510dce8a31a8fe7eabd405f4e1d68b78.poster.avif?t=1721093505\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426710/extras/510dce8a31a8fe7eabd405f4e1d68b78.webm?t=1721093505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426710/extras/510dce8a31a8fe7eabd405f4e1d68b78.mp4?t=1721093505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Easy to use (only need to control the direction of movement), super refreshing, roguelikes, fast pace (no more than 30 minutes per game).<br></li><li>Hundreds of items and summons, build different combinations.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426710/extras/72d53542b09cf14a689a8cb14078a210.webp?t=1721093505\" width=600 height=60 /></span></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426710/extras/c82f945db616549260b0c897b1755155.avif?t=1721093505\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>A doctor in a small town suddenly gained the ability to shrink his body, so he shrunk his body into various patients' bodies and treated diseases by eliminating the virus in the patients' bodies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426710/extras/5a509c6f871f83a83e97aff7af3d2286.avif?t=1721093505\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dominating Summon Combat: Although the Doctor himself has some attack ability, he mainly needs to fight through summons.<br></li><li>Cooperate with summons to trigger skills.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426710/extras/0a0e55ccb391ee845439a8c85d416633.poster.avif?t=1721093505\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426710/extras/0a0e55ccb391ee845439a8c85d416633.webm?t=1721093505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426710/extras/0a0e55ccb391ee845439a8c85d416633.mp4?t=1721093505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Each summon has its own special attack mode, which can be upgraded and synthesized to create a more powerful summon.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426710/extras/983ed675f9caedef8acbcccc4389836f.avif?t=1721093505\" width=600 height=238 /></span><br></li><li>The Doctor can choose a base weapon, and different summons will activate different characteristics of the weapon, such as ejection, explosion, burning, freezing, etc.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426710/extras/510dce8a31a8fe7eabd405f4e1d68b78.poster.avif?t=1721093505\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426710/extras/510dce8a31a8fe7eabd405f4e1d68b78.webm?t=1721093505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426710/extras/510dce8a31a8fe7eabd405f4e1d68b78.mp4?t=1721093505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Easy to use (only need to control the direction of movement), super refreshing, roguelikes, fast pace (no more than 30 minutes per game).<br></li><li>Hundreds of items and summons, build different combinations.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426710/extras/72d53542b09cf14a689a8cb14078a210.webp?t=1721093505\" width=600 height=60 /></span></li></ul>",
